data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v3-rlfgd1-375\">PG</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v4-zb06na-376\">Payment Gateway</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v4-upcoec-377\">PIC</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v4-7itkc0-378\">Person in charge</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v4-tcw3pa-379\">MDR</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v4-3834sj-380\">Merchant Discount Rate</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v4-c3igm3-381\">ABS</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v4-jfa9t5-382\">Average Basket Size</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v4-kiq14o-383\"><a id=\"_9co4lzbdd68h\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8v5-4u9gbt-384\"><a id=\"_ejxly55we75x\" display=\"false\"></a><a id=\"_d758rtuj0pwc\" display=\"false\"></a>Partner PIC</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8va-bvjpk9-405\"><em>WAG : please reach out to MO PIC to be invited to this product WAG</em></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8va-s5rdeu-406\"><strong>Name</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vb-xihlnv-407\"><strong>Email</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vb-t2bpb8-408\">Adya</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vb-tm87bk-409\"><a><u>adyanti.jatiningrum@shopee.com</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vb-iwumfo-410\">Pramuda</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vb-32oige-411\"><a><u>pramuda.wardani@shopee.com</u></a></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vb-2tve7e-412\"><a id=\"_yex1st1csmha\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vb-l2xy1s-413\"><a id=\"_owb1e8ihnjl8\" display=\"false\"></a>Eligibility</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vb-w1w607-414\"><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vb-l08vyz-415\"><strong>Can Apply for Shopeepay?</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vc-x6qs97-416\">Indonesian Entity (PT/CV/Yayasan)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vc-37as6u-417\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vc-7fmjl9-418\">Indonesian Entity (Perseroan Perorangan/PP)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vc-9iazfk-419\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vc-kn218z-420\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vd-jts2pc-421\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vd-rgdasp-422\">Foreign Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vd-yvoct9-423\">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vd-t1w032-424\"><a id=\"_ua1gk41r86em\" display=\"false\"></a>Industry Restriction</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vd-7c7zef-425\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vd-06drp8-426\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vd-4dj2sp-427\">Restricted Industry</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ol data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vd-jpvfyd-428\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vd-o5rass-429\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-a46w5y-621\">Digital Products (<strong>PPOB, Game Voucher Reseller, any wallet top up products</strong>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8ve-13pigm-430\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-t58fuo-622\">Investment (<strong>Crypto, Gold for Investment, Stocks, Trading Companies</strong>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8ve-mghkbo-431\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-hp11g2-623\">Lending (<strong>Peer to Peer, Online Loans Repayment, Koperasi</strong>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8ve-05km2b-432\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-3axuz9-624\">Non-corporate e-commerce Reseller</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8ve-st6wz7-433\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-ie497v-625\">Online-Offline POS/Online Payment Aggregator without MID Separations</p></li></ol></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8ve-4qxi4t-434\"><a id=\"_n8hr8eukzsfn\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8ve-i36ybr-435\"><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\" display=\"false\"></a>Merchant Requirements </h2><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-6x06mi-437\">Below are the requirements that merchant has to submit:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-hok6bp-438\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-o4bcrm-439\"><strong>Requirements</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-64u6en-440\">Eligible Merchants Criteria</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ol data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-hycidu-441\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-0yg40h-442\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-ap5v83-626\">Need to have high TPV, which comes from high basket size merchant</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-tqh5oh-443\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-80gy5j-627\">Industry preference from Electronics, Home Shopping, Lifestyle, E-Commerce, luxury fashion (jewellery, Branded bags, clothes, sneakers)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-txiyg1-444\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-6byfg6-628\">Have other pay later channels activated, Akulaku, Kredivo, Cicil, Indodana, and Home Credit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-ywhd2p-445\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-p58u4i-629\">Credit Card-segmented merchants</p></li></ol></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-92qatj-446\"><a id=\"_jwkgh7yptwfe\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-2ys2to-447\"><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\" display=\"false\"></a>SLA</h2><ul data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-7pdh4a-448\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-tlstoa-449\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-d39q0f-630\">New Onboarding Merchants ShopeePay Later would be need +3 days after merchant got MID-SID for assessment and whitelisting</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-kqo8n1-450\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrb-dgnjsj-631\">Existing Onboarding Merchants ShopeePay Later will have SLA 7-14 working days</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-5pucs2-451\"><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-3n5q0s-452\">Shopeepay Later has 2 types that separate as New Merchant and Existing Merchants</p><h3 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-5wox1l-453\"><a id=\"_676y6famvyzh\" display=\"false\"></a>New Merchant Onboarding Steps</h3><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vf-f5l7h3-454\"><a id=\"_qn0mmtfunx4k\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:68px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vg-2608se-455\">Category</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"68\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vg-925c0m-456\">Steps</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vg-gb56p3-457\">Action</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vg-3pbuq1-458\">Process Owner</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vg-unntp7-459\">AM/Sales Request</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"68\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vg-4donrr-460\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vg-1i70yz-461\">AM/Sales would request to  <strong>#mo-request </strong>and mention <strong>@mo-id-on-shift</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vg-t4lnsz-462\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vg-a4zh0a-463\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-sppl-image-ao1gj67k.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-9yud23-464\">AM/Sales</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-372ks8-465\">MO confirm for merchant Average Basket Size</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"68\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-91opyb-466\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-usqe10-467\">MO asking merchant Average Basket Size to requestor</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-p1nmrl-468\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-7qsxt6-469\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-sppl-image-vaivk098.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-fpks3q-470\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-owsye2-471\">MO send the submission to SPP</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"68\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-n88lol-472\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-yg8opa-473\">MO will proceed BAU with sending the submission to partner via email</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-oqjr2c-474\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vh-547jr9-475\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-sppl-image-2pvp05g7.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vi-xaxz8j-476\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrd-k5ekoo-632\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"68\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vi-r2d53m-477\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vi-4qfnkg-478\">After sending the email, MO will input the merchant details in SPayLater tab sheet</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vi-93iwxe-479\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vi-cb3clc-480\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-sppl-image-j23xtral.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vi-gq28e6-481\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vi-je17m6-482\">Feedback From Partner</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"68\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfre-8wlzgh-633\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vi-phqqki-483\">Partner will be change the status into <strong>Live</strong> on the column I</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfre-nr9xsd-634\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-h5gs89-484\"><a id=\"_fp2agn1zgl47\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h3 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-89e0lu-485\"><a id=\"_t22ddepi0q99\" display=\"false\"></a>Existing Merchants Onboarding Steps</h3><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-4pizm8-486\"><a id=\"_vzokm9iu7d5m\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-386cj3-487\">Category</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-ars259-488\">Steps</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-ocfbbb-489\">Action</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-mok0qf-490\">AM/Sales Request</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-dh4uwe-491\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-wvhljz-492\">AM/Sales would request to <strong>#mo-request </strong>and mention <strong>@mo-id-on-shift</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vj-f65030-493\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-521cth-494\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-sppl-image-z7mmr3ml.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-3qkdh7-495\">MO confirm for merchant Average Basket Size</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-moyi3o-496\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-ne92kh-497\">MO asking merchant Average Basket Size to requestor</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-9q5fkq-498\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-pogdhu-499\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-sppl-image-byppglvy.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-8lnhsk-500\">MO fulfilled the merchant details on form</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkapfrf-xr5kc0-635\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-txx1k6-501\">MO will fulfilled the merchant details on SPayLater form tab sheet</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-526reu-502\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpm8vk-a8v3ks-503\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-sppl-image-1xq43zvq.png